   <concept id="DFARS_225.770-3" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3">
      <title>
         <ph props="autonumber">225.770-3</ph> Exceptions.</title>
      <conbody>
         <p>The prohibition in 
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly" base="i1378880" href="225.770-2.dita#DFARS_225.770-2">225.770-2</xref>
             does not apply to items acquired—</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(a)  In connection with a visit to the People’s Republic of China by a vessel or an aircraft of the U.S. armed forces;</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(b)  For testing purposes; or</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(c)  For the purpose of gathering intelligence.</p>
      </conbody>
